# â˜ï¸ 4. Despliegue Manual en AWS

## 4.1 Backend --- CDK Deploy

``` bash
aws configure
cd infra
cdk bootstrap
cdk deploy
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## 4.2 Actualizar Lambdas Manualmente

### Lambda API

``` bash
zip -r lambda_api.zip .
aws lambda update-function-code \
  --function-name InfraStack-SpaceXApiLambdaD2E4A341-hpLHEvsea8DU \
  --zip-file fileb://lambda_api.zip \
  --region us-east-1
```

### Lambda Import

``` bash
zip -r lambda_import.zip .
aws lambda update-function-code \
  --function-name InfraStack-SpaceXImportLambda82D521AC-xHcGSI9T3DDu \
  --zip-file fileb://lambda_import.zip \
  --region us-east-1
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------

# ğŸŒ 4.3 Desplegar Frontend --- Docker + ECR + ECS

### Build

``` bash
docker build -t spacex-frontend .
```

### Login

``` bash
aws ecr get-login-password --region us-east-2 | docker login \
  --username AWS \
  --password-stdin 986518320161.dkr.ecr.us-east-2.amazonaws.com
```

### Push

``` bash
docker tag spacex-frontend:latest \
  986518320161.dkr.ecr.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/spacex-frontend:latest

docker push \
  986518320161.dkr.ecr.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/spacex-frontend:latest
```

### Redeploy ECS

``` bash
aws ecs update-service \
  --cluster spacex-cluster \
  --service spacex-service \
  --force-new-deployment \
  --region us-east-2
```

